{"tid":921741,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【被人叫謝仔】同拉姑探訪長者中心 四哥聞栢芝生B：冇見佢好耐","createTime":"2018-11-29T20:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T06:06:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d8fc94d6a5b44b6ccbce5e3452917d7bc857c048","tid":921741,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T20:52:17.000Z","msg":"82歲嘅謝賢今日聯同前妻狄波拉喺黃竹坑為《歡樂滿東華2018》探訪長者中心，狄波拉嘅現任老公江耀城亦有同行。<br />\n謝賢今日喺長者中心由「四哥」變咗做「謝仔」，謝賢笑言：「佢哋老過我嘛，而且我都嚟過幾次啦。」四哥話覺得長者中心嘅老人家普遍都唔鍾意笑，不過佢就話有個秘訣，就係整粒糖過佢歎咁話。而拉姑表示自己就會稱呼謝賢為四哥：「好開心㗎，全世界見到佢都會笑，佢好識呃呃氹氹。」謝賢聽到之後就笑拉姑老公江耀城：「佢最叻，呃走埋佢（拉姑）。」<br />\n講到一直肩負照顧四哥兩個孫仔謝振軒（Lucas）同謝振南（Quintus）重任嘅栢芝今日傳出誕下第三胎嘅消息，前老爺謝賢接受《蘋果》電話訪問表示：「哈哈！生咗BB？我冇見佢好耐，點知佢有冇大肚，你唔好問我啦，OK！」即匆匆收線。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181129/large/1543486122_678d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181129%2Flarge%2F1543486122_678d.jpg&h=b145c4cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181129/large/1543486123_0fac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181129%2Flarge%2F1543486123_0fac.jpg&h=0684c44f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181129/large/1543486122_383b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181129%2Flarge%2F1543486122_383b.jpg&h=7523a45e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181129/large/1543486125_b534.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181129%2Flarge%2F1543486125_b534.jpg&h=d7d7d113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181129/large/1543486306_8fab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181129%2Flarge%2F1543486306_8fab.jpg&h=242ae3bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181129/58973105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F58973105&d=%2FWF5AIj6jbqjK091Au4%2FB%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=142d81f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F58973105&h=1e784e11\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181129/58973105</a>"},{"pid":"20abf2e1a989aa5b8d192266573dbbde520d7c09","tid":921741,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}